trans-unit.source: Interacts with the parser to build a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Samhandler med parseren å bygge en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The LabelControlBuilder causes the parser to ignore inner text if it contains only white space characters.
trans-unit.target: LabelControlBuilder gjør parseren ignorerer teksten hvis den inneholder bare mellomrom.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LabelControlBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LabelControlBuilder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether white space literals are allowed.
trans-unit.target: Angir om litteraler mellomrom er tillatt.

trans-unit.source: This method overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to ignore white space in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> control.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyrer den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å ignorere mellomrom i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
